            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "RFID POLICE BADGE HOLDER WALLET: The ASR Federal credit card holder, ID and police badge holder bifold wallet comes with Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) shield technology, preventing electronic pick-pocketing and identity theft, keeping your ID and credit cards safe and secure at all times",
