                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "BADGE HOLDER: This RFID wallet police badge holder features a recessed badge cut-out design that allows badges to fit seamlessly in the wallet without any extra added bulk; mounting is pin-back or clip back (no screws required)",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SUEDE BADGE PROTECTION FLAP: The police badge holder and ID card holder features a built in suede badge protection flap to keep badges scratch free hidden from view if necessary in covert field situations; wallet also includes a removable ID card holder, cash compartment, credit card slots and built in ID card holder slot",
