        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Made from 100% genuine leather, this badge holder wallet boasts a strong and sturdy construction with reinforced stitching and a heavy gauge leather body; the badge holder will relax over time with use as it molds to your carrying habits, but will never forego its integrity and structure.<br/><br/>The ASR Federal Leather Police Bifold RFID Wallet Badge Holder with Removable ID Card Holder has been specifically designed for all private or public safety and security professionals who need their ID in one convenient location, and also for those, who at times, require discretion of their ID for undercover, covert or plainclothes operations. Importantly, the bifold wallet features Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) shield technology, preventing electronic pick-pocketing and identity theft, keeping your ID and credit cards safe and secure.<br/><br/>The ASR Federal badge holder RFID wallet features a clear removable credit card holder, as well as a built in clear ID card holder slot, a generous cash compartment, numerous credit card slots, a recessed badge cut-out mount, allowing your police badge to fit seamlessly in pockets without any extra added bulk-and lastly, an interior suede protection flap to keep badges scratch-free and add another layer of discretion when needed. <br/><br/>Badge attachment is clip-back or pin-back, no screws required. This RFID wallet is specifically designed for a shield-shaped police badge. Please measure your own personal badge to ensure it fits with this badge holder RFID leather wallet. The maximum badge size for this badge holder wallet is: 3 5/16 x 2 5/16 inches.<br/><br/>NOTE: Badge is NOT included with purchase",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
